1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,210
[Episode 56]

2
00:00:02,210 --> 00:00:03,690
Thank you so much, Max.

3
00:00:07,170 --> 00:00:10,970
Max, hello. What's wrong?
You were avoiding me yesterday too.

4
00:00:10,970 --> 00:00:14,570
Max, we're together now.
Just tell me what's bothering you.

5
00:00:14,570 --> 00:00:16,690
Max, trust me a little.

6
00:00:17,570 --> 00:00:18,770
Trust?

7
00:00:18,770 --> 00:00:23,130
All this time we've been together,
I thought what's inside matters more than looks.

8
00:00:23,130 --> 00:00:25,730
But you're disgusting inside and out.

9
00:00:26,170 --> 00:00:27,090
You slut.

10
00:00:27,210 --> 00:00:28,940
Hey, having a lovers' quarrel?

11
00:00:29,170 --> 00:00:36,810
-Slut! Slut! Slut! Slut!-
-Slut! Slut! Slut! Slut!-

12
00:00:47,730 --> 00:00:49,060
Are you trying to tell me

13
00:00:49,580 --> 00:00:53,730
that everything that happened
was just a misunderstanding?

14
00:00:56,370 --> 00:00:59,740
I'm begging you, can you forgive me?

15
00:01:01,680 --> 00:01:04,620
I was wrong. I shouldn't have distrusted you.

16
00:01:05,090 --> 00:01:10,850
Leaving you trapped
in the pain I caused.

17
00:01:15,050 --> 00:01:20,490
Bin, I'm sorry.

18
00:01:36,530 --> 00:01:38,410
An apology now,

19
00:01:40,930 --> 00:01:42,300
what good is it?

20
00:01:49,250 --> 00:01:55,850
To me,
you're just a finished chapter in my past.

21
00:01:57,130 --> 00:01:59,650
This was all just a misunderstanding.

22
00:01:59,650 --> 00:02:03,010
For eight years,
I've been living in hatred.

23
00:02:03,010 --> 00:02:06,020
And who's responsible
for all those terrible feelings?

24
00:02:06,020 --> 00:02:08,580
[To Be Continued]
